---
title: Creamy Chicken and Mushroom Pie  with Potato Topping and Roasted Carrots
description: This Creamy Chicken and Mushroom Pie  is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R01_W13_UK_R1099-7_Main_4_high-db81b667.jpg
